B.UI=new A.K("Introdu\xe7\xe3o","Last updated: July 2026")
B.Ue=new A.K("What is PerfectGest I?","A mobile business management app. Data is stored locally (SQLite). No PerfectGest cloud account for clients, estimates, or cash.")
B.Te=new A.K("Does it work offline?","Offline-first for daily use. Optional Google services (Analytics, Remote Config, minimal Firestore for subscription eligibility) may need a network when active.")
B.TF=new A.K("Can I use the app without a subscription?","Yes, to explore (browse screens and the interface). Operations (creating clients, commercial or fiscal estimates, cash entries; generating management PDFs; encrypted backup restore; and other gated actions) require Pro Plan. Trying an operation without a subscription shows a notice with the plan (reference R$ 9.90/month; price on Google Play) and Subscribe or Continue exploring app features.")
B.TU=new A.K("How does the Pro Plan work?","Monthly or annual subscription on Google Play: clients, estimates, cash and PDFs without practical limits; encrypted backup restore; interactive business card (vCard, QR, preview). Manage in Settings \u2192 Google Play subscription.")
B.Se=new A.K("Where do I manage the subscription?","Settings \u2192 Google Play subscription. Cancel via Play Store \u2192 Payments & subscriptions.")
B.RH=new A.K("What is the Quote/NF-e/NFS-e tab?","A local fiscal quote (products and services, NCM/CFOP/LC 116 codes, lookup/registration, quote PDF). When status is Approved, you can generate an NF guide PDF with technical data and official portal links. It does not issue electronic NF-e/NFS-e to tax authorities.")
B.Ti=new A.K("What is the digital business card?","In Company, edit professional business details only (not clients or cash). Share card generates a PNG via the system share sheet. After your first card, without Pro Plan the card is static (you can still share the snapshot PNG); with Pro, edit and use advanced features in the app only (vCard, QR, interactive preview) \u2014 no PerfectGest-hosted web page.\n\nClients and financial data stay protected on the device and are not sent to servers automatically.")
B.Ua=new A.K("Are my client and financial data protected?","Yes. Stored locally (including fiscal quotes). They leave the device only if you share a PDF, card PNG/vCard/QR, or an exported backup file (encrypted backup recommended on Pro).")
B.Up=new A.K("Fiscal reminders, weekly calendar, Latest entries, notifications, ads, Crashlytics, languages?","On-device fiscal reminders (informational only); weekly calendar in Company; home shortcuts to recent records; local notifications only; no ads; no Crashlytics; PT / EN / ES.")
B.Ta=new A.K("Privacy, deletion, suggestions?","Settings \u2192 Help and support for legal links. Wipe device: Settings \u2192 Data on this device \u2192 Delete all data. Feedback: Company tab \u2192 email suporte@perfectgestdev.com.")
B.a25=s([B.UI,B.Ue,B.Te,B.TF,B.TU,B.Se,B.RH,B.Ti,B.Ua,B.Up,B.Ta],t.h)
B.TL=new A.K("Introdu\xe7\xe3o","\xdaltima atualiza\xe7\xe3o: Julho de 2026\nO PerfectGest I oferece controlo claro dos dados, em conformidade com a Google Play e a LGPD. A app \xe9 local-first.")
B.RK=new A.K("Resumo","Dados de clientes e financeiros n\xe3o s\xe3o enviados automaticamente para servidores PerfectGest. S\xf3 podem sair do telem\xf3vel se partilhar PDFs, partilhar ficheiros de backup que exportou, partilhar PNG/vCard do cart\xe3o de visita ou mostrar um QR com contactos profissionais.")
B.UG=new A.K("1. Dados de gest\xe3o (local)","Armazenados em SQLite no dispositivo: clientes, or\xe7amentos comerciais, or\xe7amentos fiscais e c\xf3digos fiscais, caixa, ordens de servi\xe7o, dados da empresa (incluindo log\xf3tipo), c\xf3pia do cart\xe3o de visita, lembretes fiscais.\n\nComo eliminar\n\n- Na app: Configura\xe7\xf5es \u2192 Dados no dispositivo \u2192 Eliminar todos os dados neste aparelho\n- Android: Defini\xe7\xf5es \u2192 Apps \u2192 PerfectGest I \u2192 Armazenamento \u2192 Limpar dados\n- Desinstalar a app\n\nAviso: sem c\xf3pia externa, n\xe3o h\xe1 recupera\xe7\xe3o \u2014 n\xe3o guardamos c\xf3pias nos nossos servidores.\n\nBackups partilhados: elimine manualmente no WhatsApp, e-mail ou nuvem onde os guardou.")
B.Sj=new A.K("2. Firebase / telemetria","Metadados an\xf3nimos de instala\xe7\xe3o e m\xe9tricas de uso (elegibilidade de assinatura / anti-abuso; consumo do 1.\xba cart\xe3o). N\xe3o alojamos conte\xfado do cart\xe3o de visita nem o log\xf3tipo em servidores.\n\nE-mail: suporte@perfectgestdev.com \u2014 Assunto: Solicita\xe7\xe3o de Exclus\xe3o de Dados T\xe9cnicos")
B.Sz=new A.K("3. Notifica\xe7\xf5es locais","Canceladas ao desinstalar ou ao apagar os dados na app.")
B.Tg=new A.K("4. Prazos","Dados locais: imediato. Telemetria Firebase: at\xe9 15 dias \xfateis ap\xf3s pedido por e-mail.")
B.a26=s([B.TL,B.RK,B.UG,B.Sj,B.Sz,B.Tg],t.h)
